    "description": "<p>IKAS INTERNATIONAL (ASIA) PTE. LTD.</p>\n\n<p>iKas International was founded in 2004 in London to deliver specialist recruitment solutions into the financial services industry . Through best in class service and in-depth market knowledge, iKas has grown to be considered supplier of choice to a number of leading Financial Institutions globally.</p>\n\n<p>In 2008, iKas International launched in Asia and now have offices in Hong Kong, Singapore and Sydney and are considered one of Asia's leading banking and finance specialist recruitment agencies.</p>\n",
